name: No Contact Information
transcript: I need help with my situation. I've been living in my car for the past month because I lost my apartment. I'm in Chicago and it's getting really cold. I need shelter and I need food. I also need help finding work. This is a very difficult time for me. I'm not sure what to do next. I hope someone can assist me with getting back on track. Thank you for listening.
